Quickstrike:




It wasn't long until the repairs were finished. Quickstrike crawled out of 
the CR chamber and looked over his claws. Twice in one day wasn't his idea 
of getting around. He looked up to see Mantella. He narrowed his eyes at 
her, and said, "That's none of yer business!" He snapped his claws at her to 
back her up.

He transformed to his robot mode and walked out of the room. He paused, 
glaring at the room where they were holding Dark Mouse. Why should he care 
anymore? The Predacons---Megatron's Predacons had her. He could ask her 
later. He walked away, down the corridor. He went the direction where Black 
Arachnia had gone before he had been shot to slag eariler. He thought he 
could make up with her. He wanted to talk to her, but Dark Mouse overrided 
him logic circits.
